result.name: 潮苑餐廳

reviews.text: 質素錯，平，就腳

早餐唔錯(我個人喜歡A 餐) ，咖啡亦有水準，店內辣醬有別一般餐廳。
付款還可以用八達通。
標準的港式茶餐廳，没有特别好吃的食品也没有特别好喝的茶，座位也不太舒服，唯一可取的就是方便，價格便宜如果在别無選擇的情况下还是可以選這間餐廳。
價錢比連銷店貴、味道一般、都唔係時常滿座
食物質素好，服務員態度友善

result.name: Chiu Yuen Chiu Chow Noodle

reviews.text: One of the few places in Aberdeen with high quality of beef brisket of different types. The noodles are value of money and it was reasonably easy to get a seat even during the peak hours at lunch. The beef cake seems nice as well.

This restaurant mainly serves Chiu Chow noodles. Its handmade fish balls are very popular, even the Japanese media have introduced in their magazines. Besides, it supplies beef balls, dumplings and deep-fried fish skins ( 炸魚皮 ). The beef balls are very delicious and freshly made daily. Deep-fried fish skin is a specialty of this restaurant. It is crispy and slightly salty, many people love to eat.
Little cramped but good food and tasty
Not as good as expected.  But food is cheap n alright
You can eat many kinds of yummy noodles

reviews.text: 這是在香港仔挺有历史的潮州粉麵店，牛腩湯粉、牛杂湯粉，手打牛肉餅這几樣可以說是這家的招牌食品，味道很正宗，價錢也不算貴，出生經常滿座。唯一缺点就是鋪面有点小。值得推薦的小店
雖然感覺上比較污糟，但食物味道不差的
